               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="14v">1v-14v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s14IHA">قران, Seventh ǧuz’ (7/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>وَإِذَا سَمِعُوْا مَآ أُنْزِلَ اِلَيْ الرِّسُوْلِ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#14v">-14v</locus>وَّنَذَرُهُمْ فِيْ طُغْيَانِهِمْ يَعْمَهُوْنَ<note>In the first word, fatḥa is written below the šadda on wāw.</note>
                     </explicit>
                     <note>5:83-6:110. Red triple commas as verse markers. Ihmāl marks (rā'). Ǧuz' marker in black in the margin on fol. 1v. Few catchwords remain and they are from another hand, seemingly more recent than the matn. Repairs. Some folios torn, but not repaired.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
